Python can be used to  perform operation on file(Read and write data) on file.
There are two types of file:-
1. Text file 
2. Binary file

In text file the data is store in character format like .txt,.docx,.log etc
And in binary file the data is not stored in the form of character format but stored in another format like .png,.jpeg,.mov,.mp4 etc.

So before reading or writing the file we need to open that file for open any file in  python syntax is 

variable_name = open("file_name","mode")

Mode describe in which mode like read file or write file the default mode is read mode
